      "type": "code",
      "lang": "javascript",
      "content": "Promise.race([\n  esperar(200, 'lento'),\n  esperar(80, 'rapido')\n]).then((v) => console.log('race:', v));\n\nPromise.race([\n  esperar(80, 'boom', true),\n  esperar(200, 'ok')\n]).catch((e) => console.log('race erro:', e.message));",
